rows.label: campfev11_410_100_msg0001
rows.name: Maybe I haven't trained enough yet...

rows.label: campfev11_410_100_msg0002
rows.name:
How about you train with Kasumi
this time?

rows.label: campfev11_410_100_msg0004
rows.name:
Sure, training's great. But I think the
real problem here is strategy.

rows.label: campfev11_410_100_msg0006
rows.name:
Since Hugo and Wadatsumi are back, why
don't we all put our heads together and
see if we can refresh our tactics?

rows.label: campfev11_410_100_msg0007
rows.name:
Wadatsumi and I are at your care
Adel! Aren't we Wadatsumi!

rows.label: campfev11_410_100_msg0008
rows.name:
Indeed! We will do all we can to
lock step with you, Prince!

rows.label: campfev11_410_100_msg0010
rows.name:
When we've worked over our tactics,
let's set out on Olnard's Trail.
